  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이제</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>단상자, 싸바리 박스, 합지 박스</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d9943250-1971-4d4d-8210-075000dd7b42\" style=\"color:#555555;\">는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-536c8270-a0ec-4548-98d3-cccfdeac4be9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-536c8270-a0ec-4548-98d3-cccfdeac4be9\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MTdfMTM4/MDAxNzU1NDA3MzQ3NDQ2.IGlhWISZqqF10J_Sl-NBGn8UNk-2nGovsKLtp-tc_K0g.LZI7PQ2BeaO7kV95cvTU_c6OtzMhIAp1vjg6v6EhZ6Ag.PNG/SE-536c8270-a0ec-4548-98d3-cccfdeac4be9.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"277\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MTdfMTM4/MDAxNzU1NDA3MzQ3NDQ2.IGlhWISZqqF10J_Sl-NBGn8UNk-2nGovsKLtp-tc_K0g.LZI7PQ2BeaO7kV95cvTU_c6OtzMhIAp1vjg6v6EhZ6Ag.PNG/SE-536c8270-a0ec-4548-98d3-cccfdeac4be9.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">스펀지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">스펀지는 제품을 보호하지 좋은 소재입니다. 경도도 3가지 정도가 있어서 선택할 수 있습니다. 물론 가장 단단한 것은 스티로폼의 보드 형태로 제작이 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-64836dc6-3df1-40fb-85e8-471841d5d17b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:510px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-64836dc6-3df1-40fb-85e8-471841d5d17b\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MTdfMTQ1/MDAxNzU1NDA3Nzk0MDUz.wXfz2PF5eDTEHXTdnEOvFJAmfC7c0OKGmJtQ-OBg2LEg.3U0cnzFmPBtt32eUsBFDizJwIt00uAinlLBQ2GE-9cog.PNG/2%EB%8B%A8_%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8002.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"510\", \"originalHeight\" : \"397\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MTdfMTQ1/MDAxNzU1NDA3Nzk0MDUz.wXfz2PF5eDTEHXTdnEOvFJAmfC7c0OKGmJtQ-OBg2LEg.3U0cnzFmPBtt32eUsBFDizJwIt00uAinlLBQ2GE-9cog.PNG/2%EB%8B%A8_%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8002.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-72de4ba8-a241-443c-b1cc-478822d9e7da\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7ce2e513-6e0d-4948-81c1-6526800384fd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-75edaa26-269d-4f5c-83b9-2a3574966e8b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 스펀지는 제품을 담을 때 종이보다는 유연하여 약간의 오차도 허용되기도 하고 제작할 때 약간은 적게 목형을 제작하여 끼울 때 딱 맞물리게 제작하는 노하우로 만듭니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c19ac0f-e2c9-4a3b-b614-97f3690e26c5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9fb076fb-3089-4c42-9ead-c45c1651d82f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-33dbec09-cbd2-4ef4-b8dd-166877718425\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-588eefea-a963-453d-8244-340f588eab2d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이는 목형집의 노하우로서 제품을 직접 받아서 제작합니다. 직접 제품을 끼워 보고 수정하여 제작하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-ff1cb553-195a-457b-b920-af01fc8e1b37\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2b7be9d9-206e-41a0-ac60-38638b6ba93f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-eaa192ad-1d8b-42ea-9efb-304149f6dd85\" style=\"\">스티로폼</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6dc404a9-8dab-403e-bbf6-05d81aa4bc4c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b8b0d4a8-0f12-4b7c-b7b0-2aee012ead74\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cb2e7348-f109-4e48-95c7-1ab9e88de23f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">스펀지보다 단단한 보드 형태를 말합니다. 스티로폼은 스펀지보다는 유연하지는 않지만 단단하게 고정할 수 있고 종이보다는 더 고급스럽게 보일 수 있습니다. 물론 가격은 가장 비쌉니다. 그리고 만들 때도 더 신경 써서 제작해야 합니다. 스티로폼에도 실크인쇄를 할 수 있고 또 종이를 합지할 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0a9a4f68-9946-4343-bdf7-70cb44187f2a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:416px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0a9a4f68-9946-4343-bdf7-70cb44187f2a\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MTdfMTUx/MDAxNzU1NDA4MTQzNDc5.PlA0DlgBJ8j3iRGIIBwqGRVcXFLpq2gpCb9H4rMmlu8g.SP9MkAbHD1qLmk7zMHwJmpUNPHM2qXbxzMX1Su4sQm8g.PNG/2%EB%8B%A8_%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8005.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"416\", \"originalHeight\" : \"396\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MTdfMTUx/MDAxNzU1NDA4MTQzNDc5.PlA0DlgBJ8j3iRGIIBwqGRVcXFLpq2gpCb9H4rMmlu8g.SP9MkAbHD1qLmk7zMHwJmpUNPHM2qXbxzMX1Su4sQm8g.PNG/2%EB%8B%A8_%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8005.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-e0eb6ab7-7ebe-45ee-8450-9e4f28c8c360\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b3c718ed-e3f3-42ac-a2fa-9edf5b7cb78c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c6120c16-b982-43dd-a966-3c1270674437\" style=\"\">종이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2cbfad98-4114-43db-9729-8a499f1b2721\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dafb61da-aab1-48bc-b5e2-19c6b3382845\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2d319ec8-694e-4760-818e-c246ff03d40f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이는 가장 저렴하고 제작하기 용이합니다. 스펀지보다는 더 다양한 형태로 제작할 수 있으며 스펀지는 제품을 보호하지 좋은 소재입니다. 경도나 단단함도 정확한 형태로도 여러 가지를 만들 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0d6d70c5-7196-4fc2-a027-39e8d943ea78\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:383px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0d6d70c5-7196-4fc2-a027-39e8d943ea78\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MTdfMyAg/MDAxNzU1NDA4MDMxNTY0.ifRR7guWK63CWWzVVvkiO_4oB01JY80SGuzD_33aClkg.yM4JbM9ND14sU-6H2_xQZkRfDYBcIee9LUjr42iRSEwg.PNG/2%EB%8B%A8_%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8004.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"383\", \"originalHeight\" : \"397\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MTdfMyAg/MDAxNzU1NDA4MDMxNTY0.ifRR7guWK63CWWzVVvkiO_4oB01JY80SGuzD_33aClkg.yM4JbM9ND14sU-6H2_xQZkRfDYBcIee9LUjr42iRSEwg.PNG/2%EB%8B%A8_%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8004.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cbb508b6-093a-4b18-adbb-35a8cf7f01db\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4b1ba5a8-568b-41ba-a311-bf488c42972a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-294ed667-1c23-4259-902f-625e946d1865\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그 외에 ppt나 나무, 플라스틱으로도 제작이 됩니다. 이 패드 부분은 추후에 조금 더 자세히 사진이나 동영상으로 설명을 드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223973221837#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
